fyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKu3KfyZ.jpg&h=2e2523bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明顯嘅非緊急情況下仲可以諗超過5秒先噴胡椒襲擊無移動過嘅記者，蓄意傷害他人身體，罪犯黎，拉佢唔該"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"係人道罪行罪犯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"因為人道罪係全世界都好似得個講字<br />\n要定罪都好難<br />\n但而家每日胡亂襲擊所有人係確實嘅罪行<br />\n容易令人明白同接受"},{"pid":"c15277610cda923c2200c84b1af54e96030585c7","tid":2015301,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"17c7e7c9e42375ff586a13e9661be3e4ec002290","tid":2015301,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"e6b57aca87fc6907d409b50a1b31a034435afbaf","tid":2015301,"uid":265197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"推5"}]}